 Or, like, schizo, you know, kind of like just total disidentification to the point of, like,

13
00:00:55,060 --> 00:00:57,700
 paranoia and, you know, that kind of thing.

14
00:00:57,820 --> 00:01:04,440
 I mean, Deleuze even writes about that as a possibility, as a potentiality of that situation.

15
00:01:05,380 --> 00:01:08,540
 But I don't think fascism doesn't arise from that.

16
00:01:08,680 --> 00:01:14,400
 I think if that's the condition of possibility for life, then fascism would have to be a part

