 of that dynamic as well, right?

18
00:01:16,380 --> 00:01:17,480
 Or a possibility.

19
00:01:18,580 --> 00:01:19,880
 So, but I mean, you'd have to have...

20
00:01:19,880 --> 00:01:24,020
 I mean, because paranoia strikes me as directly leading to a kind of fascism, right?

21
00:01:24,100 --> 00:01:27,280
 You know, it's that sense of, like, I'm constantly under threat by the other.

22
00:01:27,400 --> 00:01:28,200
 Because you want to collect.

23
00:01:28,760 --> 00:01:29,480
 Yeah, you want to...

