00:01:49,240 --> 00:01:53,860
 I mean, ideally, it would lead to some version of empathy.

33
00:01:54,100 --> 00:01:57,580
 Like, not in the traditional sense, I guess.

34
00:01:57,840 --> 00:02:03,680
 But, like, just in the fact that if you don't know who you are, and if you're allowing for

35
00:02:03,680 --> 00:02:09,060
 that kind of, like, real ambiguity into the fabric of your being, then you don't know

